data.description: NEW UPDATES: The home has just been repainted as well as the sidewalk re-paved. 10k Price improvement as well!  Nestled in the heart of beautiful Pasco County, Florida, this exceptional home embodies the Sunshine State's essence of relaxation, comfort, and convenience. Your own private retreat awaits, complete with a stunning outdoor pool, surrounded by recently installed pavers that glisten in the Florida sun, creating an inviting and modern space for your enjoyment.    Safety and style harmonize within this property with new storm windows and sliders. These provide a secure and well-lit environment, ensuring your peace of mind. In 2023, new gutters were thoughtfully added, guaranteeing the home remains in pristine condition year-round.    Location is key, and this home offers it all. Just moments from the captivating Gulf of Mexico, you'll relish beachside bliss and endless waterside activities. Nearby, you'll also find a hub of shopping and stores, making daily errands a breeze. And for travelers, Tampa International Airport is conveniently located a mere 30-minute drive away.    The freedom of living without HOA fees and flood zone concerns is an enticing feature of this property. Step inside, and you'll be captivated by the master bedroom's wood-like tile flooring and the upgraded granite countertops and cabinets in both the master bathroom and the kitchen, adding a touch of luxury to your daily life.    A charming Florida room leads to your private, fenced-in, and secluded pool area, perfect for enjoying the lush surroundings. The open concept living room and kitchen create a welcoming space for gatherings, and the master bedroom boasts a generous walk-in closet.    Additional highlights include upgraded light switches throughout the home, a newly paid-off saltwater system for the pool, and a modern solar hot water heater that not only lowers energy bills but also reflects your commitment to an eco-friendly lifestyle.    Don't miss your chance to make this extraordinary Florida home your very own. Contact me today to schedule a viewing and embark on the Florida dream lifestyle.
